      <title>由于交易员将美联储降息押注推迟至 7 月，美国国债暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/treasuries-slump-as-traders-push-fed-rate-cut-bets-out-to-july</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国债下跌，十年期国债有望迎来今年最糟糕的一周，因为交易员越来越多地减少对美联储今年预期的货币宽松步伐和范围的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/treasuries-slump-as-traders-push-fed-rate-cut-bets-out-to-july</guid>
